padre &lt;unk&gt; ( italian : padre &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1977 italian drama film directed by paolo and vittorio taviani . it is based on the novel padre &lt;unk&gt; by &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; . the film was selected as the italian entry for the best foreign language film at the 89th academy awards but it was not nominated .